name: Crypto Goat as The Thing
description:
Part of a collab with Snowflake the Fox (https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/foxyzz/creations) and CryptoGoats (https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/cryptogoat/creations)

Peter is an anxious goat who thinks that is a superhero.

Likes: superhero stuff, crypto coins, sushi and play around.
Dislikes: Being without his friends and family, horror movies, and vinegar.
